to quickly and efficiently manage and respond to alerts</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: flex; \">\n        <img style=\"margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 10px; height: 25px;\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/k8s-integration-icons/loki.svg\" alt=\"\">\n        <p style=\"width: 80%; margin-top: 5px;\">Collect and ship Pod logs to Loki.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width: 50%; margin-top: 0;\">\n      <div style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: flex; \">\n        <img style=\"margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 10px; height: 25px;\" src=\"https://portefaix.grafana.net/public/app/plugins/datasource/tempo/img/tempo_logo.svg\" alt=\"\">\n        <p style=\"width: 80%; margin-top: 5px;\">Collect traces with Tempo, the high-scale distributed tracing backend</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: flex; \">\n        <img style=\"margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 10px; height: 25px;\" src=\"https://grafana.com/static/img/logos/logo-mimir.svg\" alt=\"\">\n        <p style=\"width: 80%; margin-top: 5px;\">Collect metrics with Mimir, a horizontally scalable, highly available, multi-tenant TSDB for long-term storage for Prometheus.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width: 50%; margin-top: 0;\">\n      <!--\n        <div style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: flex; \">\n        <img style=\"margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 10px; height: 25px;\" src=\"https://portefaix.grafana.net/public/plugins/grafana-incident-datasource/images/logo.svg\" alt=\"\">\n        <p style=\"width: 80%; margin-top: 5px;\">Make responding to incidents faster by automating the toilsome tasks of incident management with Grafana Incident.</p>\n      </div>\n      -->\n      <div style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: flex; \">\n        <img style=\"margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 10px; height: 25px;\" src=\"https://portefaix.grafana.net/public/app/plugins/datasource/grafana-pyroscope-datasource/img/grafana_pyroscope_icon.s